CRABBY MECH:-
       GAME STARTS -> check whether crab is in air or not---> if no--> fall to the floor..

       CRAB AT FLOOR --> IDLE --> RUNNING


        while RUNNING it checks is player in sight(range) to the crabby if yese--> move towards the playerr-->
        if player is in the range to attack --> ATTACKING
        if no--> keeps on checking for the player in sight and moving towards it 

        ATTACKING --> attack over then go to IDLE state and checks the same like [IDLE TO ATTACKING].... 